Package: tidyamplicons
Type: Package
Title: Functions to Manipulate and Visualize Amplicon Count Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Stijn Wittouck
Description: These functions are an alternative to, or at least complementary to the
    phyloseq package. They are based on the tidy data pardigm and allow for
    easier, more intuitive data access, processing and visualization. You will like
    it if you like the tidyverse way of data handling. 
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    ggplot2,
    tidyr,
    dplyr,
    stringr,
    vegan,
    phyloseq
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
